  "thag2.27:5.2": "it soon stands firm again.",
  "thag2.27:5.3": "It gains even more urgency,",
  "thag2.27:5.4": "and draws its load undeterred.",
  "thag2.27:6.1": "Even so is one accomplished in vision,",
  "thag2.27:6.2": "a disciple of the Buddha.",
  "thag2.27:6.3": "Remember me as a thoroughbred,",
  "thag2.27:6.4": "the Buddhaâ€™s rightful son."
}